Privacy Policy for Chatbot AI Assistant

Last updated: [ 01/07/2023 ]

At [ Jastaheer Technology ], we prioritize the privacy and security of our users. This privacy policy outlines the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information collected from users of our Chatbot AI Assistant. By accessing and using our Chatbot AI Assistant, you consent to the practices described in this policy.

1. Information we collect:
- Personal identification information (such as name and email address) provided voluntarily by users.
- Non-personal identification information (such as device type, browser, IP address) collected automatically when interacting with our Chatbot AI Assistant.

2. How we use the collected information:
- Personal identification information is used to customize the user experience and improve our services.
- Non-personal identification information is utilized for analytical purposes, technical administration, and to enhance the functionality of our Chatbot AI Assistant.

3. Information sharing:
- We do not sell, trade, or rent personally identifiable information to any third parties.
- We may share non-personal information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our Chatbot AI Assistant or conducting our business.

4. Security:
- We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard the user's information from unauthorized access or disclosure.
- However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

5. Cookies and analytics:
- Our Chatbot AI Assistant may use cookies, which are small files stored on the user's device to enhance the user experience and collect non-personal identification information.
- We may also use analytics tools to analyze the usage of our Chatbot AI Assistant and improve its performance.

6. Third-party websites:
- Our Chatbot AI Assistant may contain links to third-party websites. These websites have their own privacy policies, and we encourage users to review them as we do not have control over their practices.

7. Compliance with laws:
- We comply with applicable laws and regulations regarding the collection, use, and retention of personal information.

8. Children's privacy:
- Our Chatbot AI Assistant is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have collected information from a child, please contact us to remove that information promptly.

9. Changes to this privacy policy:
- We reserve the right to update or modify this privacy policy at any time without prior notice.
- It is recommended to review this policy periodically for any changes. The latest update date will be indicated at the top of this policy.

10. Contact us:
- If you have any questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy or our practices, please contact us at [ jastaheertechnology@gmail.com ].

By using our Chatbot AI Assistant, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to this privacy policy.
